Gets CFB recruiting information for a specific year (and possibly a specific team)

cfb_recruiting.Rd

If two years are provided, get cfb recruiting information based on position groups during that time period for all FBS teams.

cfb_recruiting(year, team = NULL, year2 = NULL)

Arguments

year

Year
team

Team information (optional)
year2

Year 2 (End Year) - For position group information

Examples


cfb_recruiting(2018)
